story.text:
I am a new Wiki user.  I am learning about wiki for my IT class.
I would like to create a new page as a graded assignment.
The first page will be about [[Ranger School Knowledge]]

Hi Steven, it's great that you want to learn about Wikis, but this Wiki is about [[People Projects And Patterns]] in [[Software Development]]. If you'd like a Wiki for other purposes, you can set up your own Wiki on a [[Wiki Farm]].
